intermediate_rep

Class CypWhere

  • java.lang.Object
    • intermediate_rep.CypWhere

  • public class CypWhere
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores information linking to an individual predicate contained within a WHERE clause. For example, information about a statement a.name = 'Ben' would be stored in one CypWhere object.
